**Step 1: Create FolderTreeNodeVo**

Create new file at `D:\project\pt-gitlab\collabspace\collabspace-server\src\main\java\com\yottastudios\ns\collabspace\space\vo\FolderTreeNodeVo.java`:

```java
package com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.space.vo;

import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.annotation.JsonSerialize;
import com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.shared.support.serializer.NullCollectionSerializer;
import io.swagger.v3.oas.annotations.media.Schema;
import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;
import lombok.Builder;
import lombok.Data;
import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;

import java.util.List;

@Data
@NoArgsConstructor
@AllArgsConstructor
@Builder
@Schema(name = "FolderTreeNodeVo", description = "文件夹树节点")
public class FolderTreeNodeVo {

    @Schema(description = "节点ID")
    private Long id;

    @Schema(description = "文件夹名称")
    private String name;

    @Schema(description = "子文件夹")
    @JsonSerialize(nullsUsing = NullCollectionSerializer.class)
    private List<FolderTreeNodeVo> children;
}
```

**Step 2: Add folders field to SpaceVo**

The current SpaceVo at `D:\project\pt-gitlab\collabspace\collabspace-server\src\main\java\com\yottastudios\ns\collabspace\space\vo\SpaceVo.java` has fields: spaceId, name, owner, apps.

Add a new field after `apps`:

```java
@Schema(description = "空间站下的文件夹树（仅FOLDER类型）")
@JsonSerialize(nullsUsing = NullCollectionSerializer.class)
private List<FolderTreeNodeVo> folders;
```

Make sure the import for FolderTreeNodeVo is added (it's in the same package, so no import needed).

## Context

This is for feature PXTL-2263. The `folders` field will carry the folder tree for each managed space station, so the frontend can display a folder selection tree when the user picks a target for document migration.

